解一名20多歲男疑犯到23樓一單位搜查。事件驚動街坊，於邨內瘋傳。<br />\n<br />\n元朗區議員林進接獲街坊報料後趕至進行直播。由其直播片段可見，相信他當時躲在走廊轉角位，看到兩名身穿避彈衣及戴同頭盔，分別手持散彈槍及MP5衝鋒槍的警員，在後樓梯位置把守。一會後，持MP5衝鋒槍的警員走進林進，要求他不要拍下疑犯樣貌，其他警員隨即帶同疑犯離開。林進其後乘另一升降機趕到樓下時，疑犯已被押上警車駛走。<br />\n<br />\n另一條由街坊拍攝的片段可見，多名便裝及軍裝警員押解男疑犯上警車。男疑犯未有戴上頭套，身穿黑衫及黑褲，雙手反鎖上手銬被帶走。消息指，該疑犯於昨日於天耀邨被捕，而該單位為疑犯家人寓所，警方搜出彈叉、氣槍及改槍零件等證物。《蘋果》正向警方了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n林進接受訪問時表示，已與疑犯家人聯絡，並協助處理事件，初步相信與社運事件無關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210128/NW23EV7EKZGH3HHODAYIZLJPWA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210128%2FNW23EV7EKZGH3HHODAYIZLJPWA%2F&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cUwQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=4a5ebf09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210128%2FNW23EV7EKZGH3HHODAYIZLJPWA%2F&h=bb976fb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210128/NW23EV7EKZGH3HHODAYIZLJPWA/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T23:05:31.000Z","msg":"香港究竟幾時唔俾玩氣槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383db7f3f3a194b70fdab2a0045930003b4d545c","tid":2383230,"uid":173183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T23:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又屈"},{"pid":"b21ffd551ab360b20b235d2a1373eb935582422a","tid":2383230,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T23:18:53.000Z","msg":"無晒War game撚，班黑狗無晒私伙生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f531035f15cf3a78bf2a7147177f46bce9fd6067","tid":2383230,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T23:30:39.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"0a1086594c9d433f53eeec04d053c45a36cd85f8","tid":2383230,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T23:31:55.000Z","msg":"又係李桂華？"},{"pid":"4d10b73c355898f378b8ef3